{"tid":1797380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商場便衣狗的作用=無差別借d易撞市民，引起混亂之後就拉人同打人。","createTime":"2019-12-25T11:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T11:26:56.000Z","uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcdc76b2da5f648cd4665d4ce719868db27eba12","tid":1797380,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"24/12/2019 大約晚上八點 尖沙咀海港城<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/lei88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Flei88&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=1bd98778\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/lei88</a><br />\n事發：一班便衣狗俾人識穿被市民口頭問候。一個便衣借故撞向市民，隨即想拉人，其他狗即打人。市民包圍便衣狗，之後就係以上段片的事：<br />\n<br />\n0：02畫面左邊有便衣狗應該係入係下一層上黎，然後主動打圍觀市民引起混亂再濫捕。"},{"pid":"02fcc6ca37a267fd41dfc03f3d86975bb4756744","tid":1797380,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"&lt;div style=&quot;width:100%;height:0px;position:relative;padding-bottom:178.109%;&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;<a href=\"https://streamable.com/s/lei88/dvsgg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fs%2Flei88%2Fdvsgg%22&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e0eddf07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/s/lei88/dvsgg&quot;</a> frameborder=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;100%&quot; allowfullscreen style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px;overflow:hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"},{"pid":"3e0ac4ec9ea7206d45c7279444c405ce3228f763","tid":1797380,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"又恐襲市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcd43102f8f9a9be918198b086e81f74467eb8c","tid":1797380,"uid":284642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"阻阻位，希望抽時間睇下同指教<br />\n<br />\n每一個